snippet.title: Hotel R'n'R - Launch Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
www.hotel-rnr.com

The rockstar simulator, Hotel R'n'R is out today on PlayStation VR! Sell your soul to The Devil, smash up hotels and become Infamous. Pressure from hotel staff and your own limp wrists are against you, but with over 36 weapons, and a World Tour ahead of you, it’s time to get creative.
